snippet.title: Bob the Builder: Festival of Fun PS2 Gameplay HD (PCSX2)
snippet.description:
Bob the Builder Festival of Fun PS2 Gameplay
Release Date: November 30, 2007 (EU)
Platforms: Nintendo DS, PlayStation 2, Wii
_____________________________________________
PCSX2 Settings:
Renderer: OpenGL (Hardware)
Interlacing (F5): Auto
Texture Filtering: Bilinear (PS2)
Internal Resolution: 8x Native
Anisotropic Filtering: 16x
Mipmapping: Basic (Fast)
CRC Hack Level: Automatic (Default)
_____________________________________________
My PC Specs:
CPU: Intel Core i7-4790K
GPU: GeForce GTX 1070
Ram: 16GB
OS: Microsoft Windows 10 Pro
_____________________________________________
Please leave a comment and rate it. :)
Enjoy !
